## 5. Abstract Class

```java
abstract class Shape {
    abstract void draw();
}

class Triangle extends Shape {
    void draw() {
        System.out.println("Drawing Triangle");
    }
}

public class TestAbstract {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Shape s = new Triangle();
        s.draw();
    }
}
```

